data.title: Nathan Josiah “Butterscotch” Phelps (2007
data.meta_description: Nathan Josiah “Butterscotch” Phelps, 8 years old, was called home by the Heavenly Angels due to a sudden illness of influenza on February 24, 2016.  Funeral services will be 11 a.m., Wednesday, March 2, 2016, at Greater Powerhouse Church of God in Christ 428 North Woodland Avenue, Michigan City, with Elder Dwayne Hurt...
